PrecisAuthority to enter into an AGREEMENT with the Province of NEW BRUNSWICK and LA SOCIÉTÉ D'ASSURANCE DES CAISSES POPULAIRES ACADIENNES, and another with the Province of MANITOBA and the INDUSTRIAL-ALLIANCE LIFE INSURANCE COMPANY, for the purpose of making provision for the periodic payment of income assistance to laid-off older workers.
